Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.18,0:01:57.76,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&}Darka{\3c&H000000&}ga kimi{\3c&H000000&}não кото{\3c&H000000&}vo unsotsuki{\3c&H000000&}to yonde
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.89,0:02:03.39,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Mesmo com palavras que ferem o coração
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:09.19,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}O mundo sem acreditar em você
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.19,0:02:14.95,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur4.5\3c&H000000&}Mesmo usando uma coroa de espinhos
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.24,0:02:20.70,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Eu posso ser apenas seu companheiro(a)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:26.17,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\3c&H000000&\blur4.5}Kimi no itami mo kodoku mo shitte iru kara
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:35.93,OP Roma,,0,0,0,,{\blur4.5\fad(200,580)\3c&H000000&}I'm yours
